	  when app.unix? is false.

Sat Jul 23 20:11:50 2011  Tadayoshi Funaba  <tadf@dotrb.org>

	* ext/date/date_core.c: an issue that is same as  [ruby-dev:44071].
	* ext/date/date_strftime.c: identical to [ruby-dev:44112].

